# Beyond the Scoreline: A Data Analysis of European Football 2024/25

## SQL Analysis

This folder contains SQL queries used for exploratory data analysis and football analytics on the 2024/25 European football season dataset.

The analysis focuses on:

* match outcomes
* home advantage
* possession analysis
* xG analysis
* tactical formations
* player performance
* competition-level comparisons

---

# Database Tables

| Table            | Description                        |
| ---------------- | ---------------------------------- |
| football_matches | Match results and metadata         |
| match_stats      | Match statistics and tactical data |
| player_stats     | Individual player statistics       |
| lineups          | Team formations and lineups        |

---

# Competition Coverage

```sql
SELECT
    competition_name,
    COUNT(*) AS total_matches,
    COUNT(DISTINCT home_team) AS teams,
    MIN(DATE(date_utc)) AS season_start,
    MAX(DATE(date_utc)) AS season_end
FROM football_matches
GROUP BY competition_name
ORDER BY total_matches DESC;
```

| Competition           | Matches | Teams |
| --------------------- | ------- | ----- |
| Serie A               | 380     | 20    |
| Premier League        | 380     | 20    |
| La Liga               | 380     | 20    |
| Ligue 1               | 306     | 18    |
| Bundesliga            | 306     | 18    |
| UEFA Champions League | 189     | 36    |

---

# Match Outcome Distribution

```sql
SELECT
    match_outcome,
    COUNT(*) AS total,
    ROUND(COUNT(*) * 100.0 / SUM(COUNT(*)) OVER(), 1) AS percentage
FROM football_matches
WHERE match_outcome IS NOT NULL
GROUP BY match_outcome
ORDER BY total DESC;
```

| Match Outcome | Matches | Percentage |
| ------------- | ------- | ---------- |
| Home Win      | 832     | 42.9%      |
| Away Win      | 646     | 33.3%      |
| Draw          | 463     | 23.9%      |

---

# Home Advantage by Competition

```sql
SELECT
    competition_name,
    SUM(CASE WHEN match_outcome = 'Home Win' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS home_wins,
    SUM(CASE WHEN match_outcome = 'Draw' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS draws,
    SUM(CASE WHEN match_outcome = 'Away Win' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS away_wins,
    COUNT(*) AS total_matches,
    ROUND(
        SUM(CASE WHEN match_outcome = 'Home Win' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)
        * 100.0 / COUNT(*), 1
    ) AS home_win_pct
FROM football_matches
GROUP BY competition_name
ORDER BY home_win_pct DESC;
```

| Competition           | Home Win % |
| --------------------- | ---------- |
| UEFA Champions League | 50.8%      |
| Ligue 1               | 46.7%      |
| La Liga               | 44.5%      |
| Premier League        | 40.8%      |
| Serie A               | 39.7%      |
| Bundesliga            | 38.6%      |

---

# Most Common Scorelines

```sql
SELECT
    CONCAT(fulltime_home, '-', fulltime_away) AS scoreline,
    COUNT(*) AS occurrences
FROM football_matches
GROUP BY scoreline
ORDER BY occurrences DESC
LIMIT 10;
```

| Scoreline | Occurrences |
| --------- | ----------- |
| 1-1       | 224         |
| 1-0       | 182         |
| 2-1       | 163         |
| 1-2       | 136         |
| 0-1       | 136         |

---

# Halftime vs Fulltime Analysis

```sql
SELECT
CASE
    WHEN halftime_home < halftime_away THEN 'Losing at HT'
    WHEN halftime_home = halftime_away THEN 'Drawing at HT'
    ELSE 'Winning at HT'
END AS halftime_status,
COUNT(*) AS matches,
SUM(CASE WHEN match_outcome = 'Home Win' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS ended_home_win,
ROUND(
AVG(CASE WHEN match_outcome = 'Home Win'
THEN 1.0 ELSE 0 END) * 100, 1
) AS home_win_rate
FROM football_matches
GROUP BY halftime_status
ORDER BY home_win_rate DESC;
```

| Halftime Status | Matches | Home Win Rate |
| --------------- | ------- | ------------- |
| Winning at HT   | 665     | 75.3%         |
| Drawing at HT   | 748     | 35.7%         |
| Losing at HT    | 528     | 12.1%         |

---

# Match Statistics Summary

```sql
SELECT
    ROUND(AVG(home_possession), 1) AS avg_home_possession,
    ROUND(AVG(away_possession), 1) AS avg_away_possession,
    ROUND(AVG(home_shots), 1) AS avg_home_shots,
    ROUND(AVG(away_shots), 1) AS avg_away_shots,
    ROUND(AVG(home_xg), 2) AS avg_home_xg,
    ROUND(AVG(away_xg), 2) AS avg_away_xg
FROM match_stats;
```

| Metric              | Value |
| ------------------- | ----- |
| Avg Home Possession | 50.4  |
| Avg Away Possession | 49.6  |
| Avg Home Shots      | 8.5   |
| Avg Away Shots      | 8.3   |
| Avg Home xG         | 1.64  |
| Avg Away xG         | 1.47  |

---

# Does Possession Win Matches?

```sql
SELECT
CASE
    WHEN ms.home_possession > 55 THEN 'High (>55%)'
    WHEN ms.home_possession BETWEEN 45 AND 55 THEN 'Balanced (45-55%)'
    ELSE 'Low (<45%)'
END AS possession_category,
COUNT(*) AS matches,
SUM(CASE WHEN m.match_outcome = 'Home Win' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS wins,
ROUND(
AVG(CASE WHEN m.match_outcome = 'Home Win'
THEN 100.0 ELSE 0 END), 1
) AS win_rate_pct
FROM match_stats ms
JOIN football_matches m
ON ms.match_id = m.match_id
GROUP BY possession_category
ORDER BY win_rate_pct DESC;
```

| Possession Category | Matches | Win Rate |
| ------------------- | ------- | -------- |
| High (>55%)         | 331     | 100.0%   |
| Balanced (45-55%)   | 1376    | 36.4%    |
| Low (<45%)          | 234     | 0.0%     |

---

# Best Formations by Win Rate

```sql
SELECT
    ms.home_formation AS formation,
    COUNT(*) AS matches_used,
    SUM(CASE WHEN m.match_outcome = 'Home Win' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS wins,
    ROUND(
        AVG(CASE WHEN m.match_outcome = 'Home Win'
        THEN 100.0 ELSE 0 END), 1
    ) AS win_rate_pct,
    ROUND(AVG(ms.home_xg), 2) AS avg_xg_created
FROM match_stats ms
JOIN football_matches m
ON ms.match_id = m.match_id
GROUP BY ms.home_formation
ORDER BY win_rate_pct DESC;
```

| Formation | Matches Used | Win Rate | Avg xG |
| --------- | ------------ | -------- | ------ |
| 4-4-2     | 467          | 43.7%    | 1.64   |
| 4-3-3     | 514          | 43.2%    | 1.59   |
| 4-2-3-1   | 524          | 43.1%    | 1.73   |
| 3-5-2     | 436          | 41.3%    | 1.60   |

---

# xG Overperformance Analysis

```sql
SELECT
    m.home_team AS team,
    m.competition_name,
    SUM(m.fulltime_home) AS actual_goals,
    ROUND(SUM(ms.home_xg), 2) AS expected_goals,
    ROUND(
        SUM(m.fulltime_home) - SUM(ms.home_xg),
    2) AS xg_overperformance
FROM football_matches m
JOIN match_stats ms
ON m.match_id = ms.match_id
GROUP BY m.home_team, m.competition_name
ORDER BY xg_overperformance DESC;
```

| Team              | xG Difference |
| ----------------- | ------------- |
| Borussia Dortmund | +6.36         |
| Bayern Munich     | +5.95         |
| OGC Nice          | +4.96         |
| FC Barcelona      | +3.93         |
| PSG               | +3.64         |

---

# Home vs Away Performance

```sql
SELECT
    'Home' AS side,
    ROUND(AVG(fulltime_home), 2) AS avg_goals_scored,
    ROUND(AVG(home_points), 2) AS avg_points,
    SUM(CASE WHEN match_outcome = 'Home Win' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS wins,
    COUNT(*) AS total_matches,
    ROUND(
        SUM(CASE WHEN match_outcome = 'Home Win' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)
        * 100.0 / COUNT(*), 1
    ) AS win_rate_pct
FROM football_matches
UNION ALL
SELECT
    'Away' AS side,
    ROUND(AVG(fulltime_away), 2),
    ROUND(AVG(away_points), 2),
    SUM(CASE WHEN match_outcome = 'Away Win' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END),
    COUNT(*),
    ROUND(
        SUM(CASE WHEN match_outcome = 'Away Win' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)
        * 100.0 / COUNT(*), 1
    )
FROM football_matches;
```

| Side | Avg Goals | Avg Points | Win Rate |
| ---- | --------- | ---------- | -------- |
| Home | 1.54      | 1.52       | 42.9%    |
| Away | 1.34      | 1.24       | 33.3%    |

---

# Top Goal Contributors

```sql
SELECT
    player_name,
    team,
    COUNT(DISTINCT match_id) AS matches_played,
    SUM(goals) AS total_goals,
    SUM(assists) AS total_assists,
    SUM(goals) + SUM(assists) AS goal_contributions,
    ROUND(
        SUM(goals) * 1.0
        / COUNT(DISTINCT match_id),
    2) AS goals_per_game,
    ROUND(AVG(rating), 2) AS avg_rating
FROM player_stats
GROUP BY player_name, team
ORDER BY total_goals DESC
LIMIT 20;
```

| Player                 | Team                | Goals | Assists |
| ---------------------- | ------------------- | ----- | ------- |
| Player 9               | FC Barcelona        | 16    | 2       |
| Player 10              | FC Barcelona        | 14    | 4       |
| Kevin De Bruyne        | Manchester City FC  | 11    | 11      |
| Trent Alexander-Arnold | Liverpool FC        | 11    | 7       |
| Alexander Isak         | Newcastle United FC | 12    | 4       |

